{"tid":435070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅帽人清場惹質疑　官指毋須證身份","createTime":"2017-10-14T02:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T18:09:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd65fa46fcab2857c7b02835bb62be94a7c9f59","tid":435070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171014/20182632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171014%2F20182632&d=1KxBnKZzKEj1YdruahSTgQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b238d3bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171014%2F20182632&h=642b69e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171014/20182632</a><br />\n<br />\n紅帽人清場惹質疑　官指毋須證身份<br />\n<br />\n8,519<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171014/large/14la1p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171014%2Flarge%2F14la1p6.jpg&h=3da535fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批戴紅帽代理人於佔旺清場時拆除示威者架設的障礙物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】佔旺清場當天有過百名身穿白色「I love HK」T恤、頭戴紅帽的壯漢聲稱獲授權清場，他們帶備工具包括𠝹刀及巨型剪鉗，更一度用利器指向示威者。被告之一黃浩銘多次要求執達主任交代「紅帽人」身份，但不獲理會。法官陳慶偉指出，若然黃浩銘對於代理人的身份有質疑，當時應該向法庭要求澄清，而禁制令沒有寫明需要向示威者證明代理人的身份，因現場有過百、過千人，根本難以逐一交代。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n執達主任：部份有暴力傾向<br />\n<br />\n辯方一直對於紅帽人的授權身份提出質疑，有份參與清場行動的署理助理執達主任余德信早前作供時，承認代理人並不專業，部份人更加有暴力傾向，因此在清場中途叫停代理人清拆障礙物，並且要求他們退後。余德信當時解釋代理人與示威者當天「少少失控」，擔心代理人若拆開最後防線，雙方或會發生正面衝突及肢體碰撞，發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n惟陳官在判詞中提及紅帽人與示威者當時情緒高漲並互相指罵，但並沒有對紅帽人的授權身份、或紅帽人清場時的行為加以着墨。<br />\n<br />\n該批紅帽子代理人案發當日一早便抵達彌敦道佔領區外點名報到，他們頸上繫有綠色頸繩工作證，僅寫有編號和「陸路交通運輸業大聯盟，依法治港，還路於民」的字句，但工作證上並沒蓋有原告授權印章。認罪的黃之鋒、不認罪的黃浩銘多次向執達主任詢問該批代理人的背景及所屬團體、以及是否有權清場，惟對方一律不回應。<br />\n<br />\n紅帽人包括工聯會轄下的汽車工會成員、人稱「大波Man」的反佔中常客石房有等，部份人戴上太陽眼鏡、口罩，自備𠝹刀、巨型剪鉗，當清場行動宣佈開始，他們便蜂擁而上剪斷路障索帶，其間與示威者激烈對罵，連執達主任也無法制止他們，他們最終僅出勤15分鐘便由警方接手清場。<br />\n<br />\n■記者楊思雅  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【佔旺清場】上衣寫「堅持到底」　官：顯示想留守<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n「其他人幫你坐監　痛苦好大」　 判前反思　岑敖暉：我係倖存者"},{"pid":"1408ef86c1b16f4c19a8c31ff7f84968042ddcec","tid":435070,"uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"依家判政治氾啲官大部份都有晒立場<br />\n點咩都無用 只係決定判你幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ce1239929356886969b6255c62ab0732f74bdb","tid":435070,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e18c59a6b76ab26ef1ae42efab98f84cf7c3c62","tid":435070,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅色就係炎黃賤種最強護身符"},{"pid":"7e648d3ef36a621ffb6cdbc5f3c15c4ea5daddbf","tid":435070,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅色就係炎黃賤種最強護身符"},{"pid":"25431059bb7eed02257644e1dafd0bd3b9e33ae8","tid":435070,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"有暴力傾向"},{"pid":"623702011dfcfee3536fbee789987a0cc9d4f07c","tid":435070,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"即係要比佢執走哂d野再去問法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424972089f157e7c5f466a87a9272351d01cedda","tid":435070,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"星期一開始就有堆紅帽人進入各大屋村入老人家單位抬野走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a78fc695aeaec377cc792cb548d837edb0db95","tid":435070,"uid":55043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"冇身份，咁果班人咪一樣違反清場令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999f58bd45a976dd038b6bf497d008963eff09f5","tid":435070,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:43:27.000Z","msg":"根本就請班來歷不明既支那種黎搞場姐"},{"pid":"db8291cc77613060dcfc4b9019c453104a18f2cb","tid":435070,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇身份，咁果班人咪一樣違反清場令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dff49c78285c79efc3fd05267063cb10705b94","tid":435070,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:02:10.000Z","msg":"係689 話唔競逐連任之後<br />\n呢班人亦隨之消失 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cc883200c10572cf2047c0e5b158f2153df002","tid":435070,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}